# Git workflow

- Default branch: `main`
- Prefer feature branches off `main`: `feat/gitleaks-adapter`, `fix/path-validation` (avoid committing large changes directly on `main` when collaborating)
- Keep PRs small and aligned with [PLAN.md](../../PLAN.md) todos
- Run `make check` before opening a PR
- PRs: use `gh pr create` when user asks; include Summary + Test plan

## What not to commit

- Virtualenv (`.venv/`)
- Tool caches (`.ruff_cache`, `.mypy_cache`, `.pytest_cache`)
- Generated scan reports with real project data unless sanitized fixtures in `tests/fixtures/`

## Hooks

Pre-commit enforces: trailing whitespace, YAML/TOML/JSON checks, private key detection, ruff, ruff-format, mypy on `src/`.
